<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 12:12:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人无法理解他们怎么会被指控犯有种族灭绝罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-cant-understand-how-they-could-be-accused-of-genocide/0000018c-f28c-d2f9-a3ef-f6ffb66b0000</link><description>面对海牙种族灭绝的指控，以色列人严阵以待，指出哈马斯 10 月 7 日犯下的恐怖罪行。但全球大规模暴行的受害者和肇事者名单很长，以色列人和巴勒斯坦人都无法幸免。指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:46:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-cant-understand-how-they-could-be-accused-of-genocide/0000018c-f28c-d2f9-a3ef-f6ffb66b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长本格维尔为所欲为，激怒了内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-minister-ben-gvir-does-as-he-pleases-rattling-the-netanyahu-government/0000018c-f2b8-d2f9-a3ef-f6ff3a3f0000</link><description>利库德集团消息人士称，伊塔马尔·本-格维尔正在“开展一场竞选活动”，“为他带来了强劲的民意调查结果”，这位极端主义部长成为以色列总理内塔尼亚胡最可行的替代者</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:23:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-minister-ben-gvir-does-as-he-pleases-rattling-the-netanyahu-government/0000018c-f2b8-d2f9-a3ef-f6ff3a3f0000</guid></item><item><title>“人们的误解是巴勒斯坦人不是一个民族。为了独立，他们愿意杀人，也愿意被杀”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-misconception-was-that-the-palestinians-arent-a-people/0000018c-eec3-d0b4-a7ce-ffe38ec80000</link><description>辛贝特前领导人阿米·阿亚隆（Ami Ayalon）在加沙战争十月份爆发以来的首次采访中呼吁释放所有人质以换取巴勒斯坦囚犯，其中包括马尔万·巴尔古提（Marwan Barghouti），他认为他是加沙战争结束后唯一能够领导巴勒斯坦人的人。战争结束</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:02:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-misconception-was-that-the-palestinians-arent-a-people/0000018c-eec3-d0b4-a7ce-ffe38ec80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列、加沙和国际法院：你需要知道的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/israel-gaza-and-the-international-court-of-justice-everything-you-need-to-know/0000018c-f2e8-d2f9-a3ef-f6ffb5720000</link><description>对以色列的指控是什么，它打算如何为自己辩护，什么时候会有裁决？</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/israel-gaza-and-the-international-court-of-justice-everything-you-need-to-know/0000018c-f2e8-d2f9-a3ef-f6ffb5720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军调查：以色列坦克开火引发爆炸，造成加沙六名士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-tank-fire-caused-blast-which-killed-six-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018c-f265-d206-a1af-f76d80ad0000</link><description>据调查，坦克炮弹无意中引爆了士兵们计划用来拆除哈马斯隧道的炸药。以色列国防军发言人表示，“吸取的教训已经发送给战场上的士兵”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:53:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-tank-fire-caused-blast-which-killed-six-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018c-f265-d206-a1af-f76d80ad0000</guid></item><item><title>前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾与南非代表团一起出席联合国最高法院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/former-labour-leader-jeremy-corbyn-joins-south-african-delegation-to-uns-top-court/0000018c-f267-d2f9-a3ef-f6774cf30000</link><description>作为巴勒斯坦事业的长期支持者，科尔宾自 2020 年被英国平等监督机构发现反犹太偏见在他领导下激增后被停职以来，就一直受到反犹太主义的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 08:46:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/former-labour-leader-jeremy-corbyn-joins-south-african-delegation-to-uns-top-court/0000018c-f267-d2f9-a3ef-f6774cf30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院禁止本-格维尔在抗议期间向警察发出命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-bars-ben-gvir-from-giving-police-orders-during-protests/0000018c-f24c-d206-a1af-f76ce4a30000</link><description>法院此前曾裁定，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 不应就抗议者向警方发出命令。 法院临时院长表示，本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 违反了该裁决</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 07:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-bars-ben-gvir-from-giving-police-orders-during-protests/0000018c-f24c-d206-a1af-f76ce4a30000</guid></item><item><title>在北部边境，以色列未能将战术胜利转化为战略收益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/on-northern-border-israel-fails-to-translate-tactical-victories-into-strategic-gains/0000018c-eff1-d312-addf-eff314b30000</link><description>以色列国防军对真主党的袭击使该组织的精锐拉德万部队稍微远离边境，但该组织仍在设法进行日常袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 04:07:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/on-northern-border-israel-fails-to-translate-tactical-victories-into-strategic-gains/0000018c-eff1-d312-addf-eff314b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；美英在红海击落21架无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-live/blinken-netanyahu-denies-gaza-transfer-as-israeli-policy-idf-probes-six-soldiers-death/0000018c-f15e-d206-a1af-f77ef4de0000</link><description>美国和英国军队击落了胡塞武装发射的 21 架无人机和导弹 ■ 以色列国防军公布在加沙战斗中阵亡士兵的姓名 ■ 布林肯在拉马拉会见巴勒斯坦权力机构主席阿巴斯 ■ 白宫表示“我们目前不支持停火” ■ 南非任命前英国反对党领袖杰里米·科尔宾为国际法院代表团成员</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-live/blinken-netanyahu-denies-gaza-transfer-as-israeli-policy-idf-probes-six-soldiers-death/0000018c-f15e-d206-a1af-f77ef4de0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党精准先例：使用反坦克导弹狙击以色列住宅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollahs-precision-precedent-sniping-at-israeli-homes-using-antitank-missiles/0000018c-efe2-d312-addf-efe20a870000</link><description>据信真主党是第一个使用精确反坦克导弹瞄准民用建筑的组织。数十座以色列建筑遭到直接袭击——现在甚至连没有撤离的城镇也在射程之内</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 02:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollahs-precision-precedent-sniping-at-israeli-homes-using-antitank-missiles/0000018c-efe2-d312-addf-efe20a870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部城市市长致内塔尼亚胡：允许高中生进行枪械训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-southern-israeli-city-to-netanyahu-allow-firearm-training-for-high-schoolers/0000018c-ef2f-d7da-adac-ff3f2eb30000</link><description>加特镇市长阿维拉姆·达哈里 (Aviram Dahari) 写道，该市“希望在以色列人民为家园而战的日子里成为实施这项非常基础的训练的先锋”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:23:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-southern-israeli-city-to-netanyahu-allow-firearm-training-for-high-schoolers/0000018c-ef2f-d7da-adac-ff3f2eb30000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：针对以色列的种族灭绝指控“毫无根据”；必须允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/blinken-genocide-charge-against-israel-meritless-palestinians-must-be-allowed-return/0000018c-ef8f-da6b-abdd-ffcf48d60000</link><description>布林肯在周二与以色列官员会面后的新闻发布会上发表了讲话。与此同时，美国和以色列在加沙的未来问题上仍存在严重分歧 — — 特别是关于重振巴勒斯坦权力机构的潜在作用，布林肯将于周三会见该权力机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/blinken-genocide-charge-against-israel-meritless-palestinians-must-be-allowed-return/0000018c-ef8f-da6b-abdd-ffcf48d60000</guid></item><item><title>“当我们无法同情巴勒斯坦人时，我们怎么能指望其他人同情我们呢？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-09/ty-article-podcast/.premium/how-can-we-expect-others-to-empathize-with-us-if-we-fail-to-empathize-with-palestinians/0000018c-ef0a-d7da-adac-ff1b816a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 17:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-09/ty-article-podcast/.premium/how-can-we-expect-others-to-empathize-with-us-if-we-fail-to-empathize-with-palestinians/0000018c-ef0a-d7da-adac-ff1b816a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属在布林肯面前示威，试图阻止对加沙的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-attempt-to-block-aid-into-gaza-protest-in-front-of-blinken/0000018c-eea8-d7da-adac-feb940080000</link><description>“我们的政府没有履行其使命。我们需要美国的紧急帮助，我们需要人质现在活着回家。我们为什么现在在这里？我们的亲人被关押在加沙 100 天之后，”拥有美国和以色列双重国籍的齐皮·海托夫斯基 (Tsipi Haitovski) 在抗议活动中说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 16:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-attempt-to-block-aid-into-gaza-protest-in-front-of-blinken/0000018c-eea8-d7da-adac-feb940080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列声称在数十次跨境袭击中杀死了真主党无人机负责人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hezbollah-exchange-dozens-of-cross-border-strikes-on-tuesday/0000018c-ee36-d7da-adac-fe375bbb0000</link><description>真主党从黎巴嫩向以色列国防军基地发射爆炸性无人机，而以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击导致三名真主党战士死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 15:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hezbollah-exchange-dozens-of-cross-border-strikes-on-tuesday/0000018c-ee36-d7da-adac-fe375bbb0000</guid></item><item><title>接地：以色列人目前不属于世界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</link><description>特拉维夫的本古里安国际机场空无一人，外国航空公司没有航班飞往这里，以色列人只是梦想着度假</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</guid></item><item><title>“当以色列与哈马斯战争爆发时，Apple TV 要求停止编写剧本”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000</link><description>近年来，以色列电视剧越来越受欢迎，广播公司与外国同行达成了协议。但自从战争爆发以来，合作就被冻结了。一位生产商警告说：“我们很可能会变得像俄罗斯一样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000</guid></item><item><title>新调查显示，一名荷兰国民在 2008 年破坏了伊朗核计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/a-dutch-national-sabotaged-irans-nuclear-program-in-2008-new-investigation-reveals/0000018c-ee18-d0b4-a7ce-ff7bc9ec0000</link><description>Stuxnet 是一种导致伊朗核计划瘫痪的恶意软件，据信是由一​​名伊朗工程师释放的。一份具有里程碑意义的新报告显示，这是一名荷兰国民——与摩萨德和中央情报局合作</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/a-dutch-national-sabotaged-irans-nuclear-program-in-2008-new-investigation-reveals/0000018c-ee18-d0b4-a7ce-ff7bc9ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯进入新的战争阶段，但仍没有加沙战后计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/phase-three-of-the-war-has-begun-and-israel-still-doesnt-have-a-postwar-plan-for-gaza/0000018c-ed7b-d89f-adcc-fffbd7e10000</link><description>美国和埃及都对未来的加沙政府提出了合法的想法，但以色列似乎拒绝讨论“以色列持续安全控制”之外的未来。战争进入第四个月，未来与战争开始时一样悬而未决</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/phase-three-of-the-war-has-begun-and-israel-still-doesnt-have-a-postwar-plan-for-gaza/0000018c-ed7b-d89f-adcc-fffbd7e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会释放人质：我看到他们伤害被囚禁的妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</link><description>“我们确切地知道他们在 10 月 7 日做了什么。如果他们有能力做到这一点——他们在 90 天内能做什么？” 19 岁丹妮拉·吉尔博亚 (Daniela Gilboa) 在加沙地带被哈马斯扣为人质，她的母亲说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</guid></item></channel></rss>